SECTION 11: LOGROTATE (AUTOMATION TOOL)

Purpose:
	•	Prevent logs from growing infinitely

⸻

Config:

/var/log/websrv-02/rsyslog_sshd.log {
daily
rotate 30
compress
}

Explanation:
	•	daily → rotate every day
	•	rotate 30 → keep 30 old logs
	•	compress → save space

⸻

Advanced config includes hashing:

sha256sum → ensures integrity

⸻

Manual run:
sudo logrotate -f config_file

⸻

